    Remove Facility
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <input type="hidden" value="" id="confirmation_pcltf_id">
    <p>
    Do you really want to remove this facility?
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="actions">
    <div class="ui cancel button" id="confirmation_cancel_pcltf">
